title: Khloe Kardashian Is Flying to Lamar Odom's Side in Las Vegas
text: Khloe Kardashian is reportedly expected to fly to be by her ex-husband Lamar Odom ‘s side in the hospital in Las Vegas, where he is getting treatment after being found unconscious on Tuesday afternoon (October 13). The 31-year-old reality star has been told about his condition and she is preparing for her trip to Vegas, according [...] »
